[00:08.35]I rise with the fire of the morning light
[00:13.71]Called to lead, called to guard the fight
[00:19.08]I carry warmth, I carry weight
[00:24.45]Learning love means more than strength
[00:29.81]I glow when the night feels long and deep
[00:35.18]Holding peace while the world sleeps
[00:40.55]I don’t hide the light I show
[00:45.91]I know how to let it flow
[00:51.28]Different callings, different ways
[00:56.65]Still we move by heaven’s grace
[01:02.01]Like the sun and moon in the same sky
[01:07.38]We don’t compete, we align
[01:12.75]I shine, you reflect the truth
[01:18.11]He leads, she brings the light through
[01:23.48]Different rhythms, perfect tune
[01:28.85]That’s how the sun loves the moon
[01:34.21]The sun says “go,” the moon says “stay”
[01:39.58]One builds the road, one makes it safe
[01:44.95]One stands bold, one stands near
[01:50.31]Together we calm each other’s fear
[01:55.68]When I burn too hot, you cool my flame
[02:01.05]When you doubt, I speak your name
[02:06.41]You remind me who I am
[02:11.78]I remind you where we stand
[02:17.15]Not above you, not behind
[02:22.52]Side by side in God’s design
[02:27.88]Like the sun and moon in the same sky
[02:33.25]Faithful through the passing time
[02:38.62]One gives light, one gives peace
[02:43.98]Both are how the darkness leaves
[02:49.35]Same promise, different tune
[02:54.72]That’s how the sun loves the moon
[03:00.08]So when the day fades into night
[03:05.45]We still move by the same light
[03:10.82]Every season, every phase
[03:16.18]We’re reflecting heaven’s ways
